{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.1","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:1","prev_osis_id":"Exod.031.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le veau d\u2019or<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. (Ps 106:19-22. Ac 7:39-41.) 1 R 12:26-33.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Le peuple, voyant que Mo\u00efse tardait \u00e0 descendre de la montagne, s\u2019assembla autour d\u2019Aaron, et lui dit: Allons! fais-nous un dieu qui marche devant nous, car ce Mo\u00efse, cet homme qui nous a fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, nous ne savons ce qu\u2019il est devenu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.2","name":"Exode 32:2","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.31.18","name":"Exode 31:18","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.31.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.2","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:2","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Aaron leur dit: Otez les anneaux d\u2019or qui sont aux oreilles de vos femmes, de vos fils et de vos filles, et apportez-les-moi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.3","name":"Exode 32:3","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.1","name":"Exode 32:1","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.3","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:3","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Et tous \u00f4t\u00e8rent les anneaux d\u2019or qui \u00e9taient \u00e0 leurs oreilles, et ils les apport\u00e8rent \u00e0 Aaron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.4","name":"Exode 32:4","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.2","name":"Exode 32:2","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.4","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:4","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Il les re\u00e7ut de leurs mains, jeta l\u2019or dans un moule, et fit un veau en fonte. Et ils dirent: Isra\u00ebl! Voici ton dieu, qui t\u2019a fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.5","name":"Exode 32:5","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.3","name":"Exode 32:3","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.5","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:5","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Lorsqu\u2019Aaron vit cela, il b\u00e2tit un autel devant lui, et il s\u2019\u00e9cria: Demain, il y aura f\u00eate en l\u2019honneur de l\u2019\u00c9ternel!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.6","name":"Exode 32:6","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.4","name":"Exode 32:4","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.6","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:6","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Le lendemain, ils se lev\u00e8rent de bon matin, et ils offrirent des holocaustes et des sacrifices d\u2019actions de gr\u00e2ces. Le peuple s\u2019assit pour manger et pour boire; puis ils se lev\u00e8rent pour se divertir.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.7","name":"Exode 32:7","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.5","name":"Exode 32:5","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.7","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:7","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-14: cf. (De 9:8-14, 25-29. Ps 106:23.) No 14:11-20.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Mo\u00efse: Va, descends; car ton peuple, que tu as fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, s\u2019est corrompu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.8","name":"Exode 32:8","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.6","name":"Exode 32:6","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.8","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:8","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Ils se sont promptement \u00e9cart\u00e9s de la voie que je leur avais prescrite; ils se sont fait un veau en fonte, ils se sont prostern\u00e9s devant lui, ils lui ont offert des sacrifices, et ils ont dit: Isra\u00ebl! voici ton dieu, qui t\u2019a fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.9","name":"Exode 32:9","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.7","name":"Exode 32:7","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.9","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:9","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Mo\u00efse: Je vois que ce peuple est un peuple au cou roide.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.10","name":"Exode 32:10","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.8","name":"Exode 32:8","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.10","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:10","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Maintenant laisse-moi; ma col\u00e8re va s\u2019enflammer contre eux, et je les consumerai; mais je ferai de toi une grande nation.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.11","name":"Exode 32:11","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.9","name":"Exode 32:9","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.11","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:11","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Mo\u00efse implora l\u2019\u00c9ternel, son Dieu, et dit: Pourquoi, \u00f4 \u00c9ternel! Ta col\u00e8re s\u2019enflammerait-elle contre ton peuple, que tu as fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte par une grande puissance et par une main forte?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.12","name":"Exode 32:12","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.10","name":"Exode 32:10","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.12","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:12","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Pourquoi les \u00c9gyptiens diraient-ils: C\u2019est pour leur malheur qu\u2019il les a fait sortir, c\u2019est pour les tuer dans les montagnes, et pour les exterminer de dessus la terre? Reviens de l\u2019ardeur de ta col\u00e8re, et repens-toi du mal que tu veux faire \u00e0 ton peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.13","name":"Exode 32:13","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.11","name":"Exode 32:11","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.13","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:13","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Souviens-toi d\u2019Abraham, d\u2019Isaac et d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, tes serviteurs, auxquels tu as dit, en jurant par toi-m\u00eame: Je multiplierai votre post\u00e9rit\u00e9 comme les \u00e9toiles du ciel, je donnerai \u00e0 vos descendants tout ce pays dont j\u2019ai parl\u00e9, et ils le poss\u00e9deront \u00e0 jamais.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.14","name":"Exode 32:14","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.12","name":"Exode 32:12","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.14","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:14","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Et l\u2019\u00c9ternel se repentit du mal qu\u2019il avait d\u00e9clar\u00e9 vouloir faire \u00e0 son peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.15","name":"Exode 32:15","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.13","name":"Exode 32:13","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.15","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:15","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-24: cf. De 9:15-17, 20, 21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Mo\u00efse retourna et descendit de la montagne, les deux tables du t\u00e9moignage dans sa main; les tables \u00e9taient \u00e9crites des deux c\u00f4t\u00e9s, elles \u00e9taient \u00e9crites de l\u2019un et de l\u2019autre c\u00f4t\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.16","name":"Exode 32:16","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.14","name":"Exode 32:14","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.16","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:16","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Les tables \u00e9taient l\u2019ouvrage de Dieu, et l\u2019\u00e9criture \u00e9tait l\u2019\u00e9criture de Dieu, grav\u00e9e sur les tables.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.17","name":"Exode 32:17","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.15","name":"Exode 32:15","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.17","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:17","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Josu\u00e9 entendit la voix du peuple, qui poussait des cris, et il dit \u00e0 Mo\u00efse: Il y a un cri de guerre dans le camp.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.18","name":"Exode 32:18","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.16","name":"Exode 32:16","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.18","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:18","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Mo\u00efse r\u00e9pondit: Ce n\u2019est ni un cri de vainqueurs, ni un cri de vaincus; ce que j\u2019entends, c\u2019est la voix de gens qui chantent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.19","name":"Exode 32:19","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.17","name":"Exode 32:17","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.19","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:19","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Et, comme il approchait du camp, il vit le veau et les danses. La col\u00e8re de Mo\u00efse s\u2019enflamma; il jeta de ses mains les tables, et les brisa au pied de la montagne.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.20","name":"Exode 32:20","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.18","name":"Exode 32:18","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.20","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:20","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Il prit le veau qu\u2019ils avaient fait, et le br\u00fbla au feu; il le r\u00e9duisit en poudre, r\u00e9pandit cette poudre \u00e0 la surface de l\u2019eau, et fit boire les enfants d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.21","name":"Exode 32:21","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.19","name":"Exode 32:19","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.21","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:21","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Mo\u00efse dit \u00e0 Aaron: Que t\u2019a fait ce peuple, pour que tu l\u2019aies laiss\u00e9 commettre un si grand p\u00e9ch\u00e9?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.22","name":"Exode 32:22","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.20","name":"Exode 32:20","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.22","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:22","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Aaron r\u00e9pondit: Que la col\u00e8re de mon seigneur ne s\u2019enflamme point! Tu sais toi-m\u00eame que ce peuple est port\u00e9 au mal.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.23","name":"Exode 32:23","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.21","name":"Exode 32:21","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.23","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:23","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Ils m\u2019ont dit: Fais-nous un dieu qui marche devant nous; car ce Mo\u00efse, cet homme qui nous a fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, nous ne savons ce qu\u2019il est devenu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.24","name":"Exode 32:24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.22","name":"Exode 32:22","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.24","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:24","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Je leur ai dit: Que ceux qui ont de l\u2019or, s\u2019en d\u00e9pouillent! Et ils me l\u2019ont donn\u00e9; je l\u2019ai jet\u00e9 au feu, et il en est sorti ce veau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.25","name":"Exode 32:25","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.23","name":"Exode 32:23","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.25","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:25","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.026,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 25-29: cf. No 25. De 33:8-11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Mo\u00efse vit que le peuple \u00e9tait livr\u00e9 au d\u00e9sordre, et qu\u2019Aaron l\u2019avait laiss\u00e9 dans ce d\u00e9sordre, expos\u00e9 \u00e0 l\u2019opprobre parmi ses ennemis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.26","name":"Exode 32:26","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.24","name":"Exode 32:24","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.26","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:26","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Mo\u00efse se pla\u00e7a \u00e0 la porte du camp, et dit: A moi ceux qui sont pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel! Et tous les enfants de L\u00e9vi s\u2019assembl\u00e8rent aupr\u00e8s de lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.27","name":"Exode 32:27","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.25","name":"Exode 32:25","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.27","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:27","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Il leur dit: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Que chacun de vous mette son \u00e9p\u00e9e au c\u00f4t\u00e9; traversez et parcourez le camp d\u2019une porte \u00e0 l\u2019autre, et que chacun tue son fr\u00e8re, son parent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.28","name":"Exode 32:28","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.26","name":"Exode 32:26","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.28","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:28","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Les enfants de L\u00e9vi firent ce qu\u2019ordonnait Mo\u00efse; et environ trois mille hommes parmi le peuple p\u00e9rirent en cette journ\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.29","name":"Exode 32:29","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.27","name":"Exode 32:27","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.29","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:29","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Mo\u00efse dit: Consacrez-vous aujourd\u2019hui \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, m\u00eame en sacrifiant votre fils et votre fr\u00e8re, afin qu\u2019il vous accorde aujourd\u2019hui une b\u00e9n\u00e9diction.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.30","name":"Exode 32:30","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.28","name":"Exode 32:28","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.30","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:30","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.031,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 30-35: cf. De 9:18-20, 25-29. Ja 5:16. Ps 99:6, 8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Le lendemain, Mo\u00efse dit au peuple: Vous avez commis un grand p\u00e9ch\u00e9. Je vais maintenant monter vers l\u2019\u00c9ternel: j\u2019obtiendrai peut-\u00eatre le pardon de votre p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.31","name":"Exode 32:31","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.29","name":"Exode 32:29","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.31","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:31","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Mo\u00efse retourna vers l\u2019\u00c9ternel et dit: Ah! Ce peuple a commis un grand p\u00e9ch\u00e9. Ils se sont fait un dieu d\u2019or.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.32","name":"Exode 32:32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.30","name":"Exode 32:30","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.32","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:32","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Pardonne maintenant leur p\u00e9ch\u00e9! Sinon, efface-moi de ton livre que tu as \u00e9crit.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.33","name":"Exode 32:33","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.31","name":"Exode 32:31","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.33","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:33","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel dit \u00e0 Mo\u00efse: C\u2019est celui qui a p\u00e9ch\u00e9 contre moi que j\u2019effacerai de mon livre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.34","name":"Exode 32:34","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.32","name":"Exode 32:32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.34","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:34","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.032.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Va donc, conduis le peuple o\u00f9 je t\u2019ai dit. Voici, mon ange marchera devant toi, mais au jour de ma vengeance, je les punirai de leur p\u00e9ch\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.35","name":"Exode 32:35","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.33","name":"Exode 32:33","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.35","label":"","reference":"Exode 32:35","prev_osis_id":"Exod.032.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Exod.033.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Exod.32.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9ternel frappa le peuple, parce qu\u2019il avait fait le veau, fabriqu\u00e9 par Aaron.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Exod.32","name":"Exode 32","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.33.1","name":"Exode 33:1","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.33.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Exod.32.34","name":"Exode 32:34","id":"fra-LSG:Exod.32.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81ef2ab7ce3.41635710');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81ef2ab7ce3.41635710\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81ef2ab7ce3.41635710","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81ef2ab7ce3.41635710'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81ef2ab7ce3.41635710\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}